700963f-a.text:
Eastchester Road, at the N.W. corner of Waring Avenue, showing the Calvary Lutheran Church. The church consists of the 2-story building facing on Eastchester Road, and a 1-story building on Waring
Avenue (left).
May 11, 1938.
P. L. Sperr.
